1 ZIA

  zeroes a fullword array

  FORTRAN Calling Sequence:  ZIA( OUT, NWORDS)

  Arguments:  OUT is the array to be cleared
              NWORDS is word (4-byte!) count to be cleared
2 Operation

  ZIA calls the C-subroutine memset to zero the array.

